name: DO NOT TRANSFORM YOUR ROAD INTO GARBAGE
description:
I WAS GOING BACK HOME, IN THE MIDDLE OF A LONG ROAD TO THE LIMIT BTW CHILE AND ARGENTINA. I WAS ON A BUS AND I START TO TAKE PICTURES FROM THE WINDOW, SOMETHING APPEAR AND I DIDNT DOUBT TO SHOOT THAT.
I GOT A LESSON, A LIFE LESSON.

IF YOU WANT TO SUCCES, PLAY A CLEAN GAME.
IF YOU WANT TO SUCCES, READ EVERY LETTER THAT YOUR ROAD SHOWS YOU.
IF YOU WANT TO SUCCES IN LIFE, DO NOT SMUSH ANY HEAD.
DONT TO BE A FOOL THINKING THAT MAYBE YOU WILL BE SUCCESFULL SUCKING OTHERS ENERGY!

HELP TO GROW UP YOUR OTHERS OR GO BACK!

DO NOT TRANSFORM YOUR ROAD INTO GARBAGE.
BE MORE THAN SMART, HELP OTHERS TO GROW UP.
